List of packages to install 


***** Qgis and its libraries (gdal, ogr)
sudo apt-get install qgis

***** Orfeo Toolbox library (to use it with command lines)
sudo aptitude install add-apt-repository
sudo apt-add-repository ppa:ubuntugis/ubuntugis-unstable
sudo aptitude install otb-bin otb-bin-qt python-otb

***** Anaconda2
https://www.continuum.io/downloads
bash Anaconda2-4.3.1-Linux-x86_64.sh 

***** Sen2cor (once anaconda is downloaded)
http://step.esa.int/thirdparties/sen2cor/2.3.1/[L2A-SUM]%20S2-PDGS-MPC-L2A-SUM%20[2.3.0].pdf  (p.33)

***** Create an account on PEPS to download the 1C Sentinel-2 images 
https://peps-mission.cnes.fr/en/peps-0

***** rasterstats
sudo apt-get install python-numpy python-gdal
pip install rasterstats
